** Our commitment to inclusion and belonging **

At Powerlink, we champion inclusion and belonging by supporting every
candidate during the recruitment journey. Please inform us of any needs or
adjustments for a more inclusive process, including sharing your preferred
pronouns. As a Veteran-Friendly Employer, we value the skills Veterans bring
and ensure equal opportunities. Let us know if you're a Veteran for tailored
support.  
Successful applicants will undergo necessary pre-employment checks. As
advocates of the Circle Back initiative, we pledge to respond to all
applications promptly.

